title: tour: typo in french Go tour
body:
The code on http://go-tour-fr.appspot.com/#3
doesn't compile:

prog.go:5: imported and not used: "net"
prog.go:6: imported and not used: "os"
 [process exited with non-zero status]


The english Go tour is OK:
http://tour.golang.org/#3

I'm not sure it's the correct place to report this problem...
